Removes sugar from Google Search results letting you focus on the important content

Nowadays, Google complements the classic results with lots of info, such as suggestions, related searches, ads, maps, videos, and so on. If you feel lost in the Google search results page, this extension can help you.

This Chrome extension helps you focusing in the actual results of the search and clears everything else. It is also a good compromise for users looking for a more accessible search page, since the typefaces are bigger, and the results take more space from the screen width.

The news and video pages are also simplified and have been get lots of extra content removed for easier comprehension and navigation.

To sum up, this extension is ideal for people who wants to focus on search results, people having sight limitations or people who find difficult to process lots of information.